metadata.name: Matter of Time 1/25
metadata.description:
In a world where the future belongs to those who rewrite the past, a team of young officers must fight to expose the truth and bring down a corrupt corporation. As they delve deeper into the shadows of power, they realize their own pasts may be more intertwined with the corporation's dark history than they ever imagined. Together they navigate the dangers of time travel technology while opposing the very forces who wish to control it, in the ultimate game of manipulation.
